name: 米歇尔·L·金
name_full: 米歇尔·L·金 Michelle L. King
introduction: Michelle L King began acting as a child and has remained active her entire life, participating in dozens of theatrical productions, hosting and emceed events. In the past several years she's added films and commercials to her resume. She has directed and taught Youth drama teams as well as being involved behind the scenes in independent movies as asst director, script supervisor, casting assistant, makeup artist and various other jobs. Michelle and her husband live on a small hobby farm with her children.
